Robert S. Wiesenthal - Wikipedia





















 






Robert S. Wiesenthal

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Rob Wiesenthal


Born
(1966-06-22) June 22, 1966 (age 51)


Residence
New York City, New York


Nationality
American


Alma mater
University of Rochester (B.A.)


Title
Founder and CEO of BLADE


Board member of

TripAdvisor[1]
STARZ [2]


