Insider Activity


Individual




Robert S. Wiesenthal



Mr. Robert S. Wiesenthal is Independent Director at Starz, Independent Director at TripAdvisor, Inc. and Chief Executive Officer at Fly Blade, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at AliphCom Corp., Starz, TripAdvisor, Inc., 3net Ltd. and The Hamptons International Film Festival. Mr. Wiesenthal was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer by Warner Music Group Corp., Chief Strategy Officer & Executive Vice President by Sony Broadband Entertainment, Chief Strategy Officer & Executive Vice President by Sony Entertainment Television India Ltd., Independent Director by Entercom Communications Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Sony Corp. of America, Director & President-International Division by Sony/ATV Music Publishing LLC, MD, Head-Entertainment & Digital Media by Credit Suisse First Boston Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Sony Corp., Chief Strategy Officer & Executive Vice President by Sony Entertainment, Inc., and Member-Operating Committee by Sony Pictures Entertainment, Inc. He also served on the board at EMI Music Publishing Group North America Holdings, Inc., Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer, Inc., Panavision, Inc., Sony Mobile Communications (USA), Inc., Sony Music Holdings, Inc. and Starz LLC. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Rochester.



